    FROM [BussinessEntities] AS [b]
    ORDER BY [b].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
